\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ and from Your people, who gave willingly. The meaning is: With mine I am familiar and I know it 
\lang1033\ltrch\f0\fs36\b0\i0\ul0\cf0\cb8\ well, but that of others I do not know, but I saw that they donated joyously, I say... \lang1033\ltrch\f2\fs36\b\i0\ul0\cf2\cb10\ and now, Your 
